io\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 776, \"end\": 781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.8719620234047741, \"rank\": 0.14683892942480894, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Swimmer Peaty last month fell agonisingly short in his attempt to achieve a similar feat in the 100m breaststroke after he was forced to settle for joint silver in the French capital behind Italian Nicolo Martinenghi.\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 1001, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 952, \"end\": 958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8634634983640992, \"rank\": 0.15433116342910563, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 974, \"end\": 981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.8204263632820641, \"rank\": 0.2037060922272131, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 982, \"end\": 1000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicol\\u00f2_Martinenghi\", \"score\": 0.9999999871768069, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nicolo Martinenghi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicol\\u00f2_Martinenghi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicol\\u00f2_Martinenghi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This time around, I am probably not going in as the absolute favourite, as maybe I was in Tokyo,\\\" Smith told the PA news agency.\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1094, \"end\": 1099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.8719620234047741, \"rank\": 0.14683892942480894, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There are probably about five or six athletes that could quite easily challenge in the BC1, which is probably the first time ever it's been that competitive - that's exciting.\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1222, \"end\": 1225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BC1\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BC1\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BC1\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BC1\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have medalled at every tournament for the last four years.\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1373, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel like it would be wrong for me not to expect that, I guess.\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1439, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I am not putting myself under (the pressure of) 'I must win it'.\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1510, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To go three in a row, Adam Peaty showed how hard that is to do.\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1574, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1533, \"end\": 1543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have got bags of energy so we will see what that turns up and as long as I can play well and put on a show for the crowd then I will be relatively satisfied.\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1736, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am in a good place and raring to go.\\\"\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1776, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Smith has won five medals across four Paralympics, beginning with team gold in 2008 in Beijing followed by two silvers at London 2012.\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1912, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1865, \"end\": 1872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999990414594369, \"rank\": 9.585415349589672e-07, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1900, \"end\": 1911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Paralympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999940883, \"rank\": 5.8395521029522715e-12, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Paralympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Paralympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Eastleigh-born athlete, who recently regained world number one status, faces stiff competition in his quest to add to the medal tally from the likes of Thailand's Witsanu Huadpradit, Muhamad Syafa of Indonesia, Dutchman Daniel Perez and Portuguese player Andre Ramos.\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 2185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2070, \"end\": 2078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8356699999859241, \"rank\": 0.19663629583510395, \"text\": \"Thailand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2081, \"end\": 2099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Witsanu_Huadpradit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Witsanu Huadpradit\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Witsanu_Huadpradit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Witsanu_Huadpradit\"}, {\"begin\": 2118, \"end\": 2127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia_national_badminton_team\", \"score\": 0.8790718859112837, \"rank\": 0.13182611849665993, \"text\": \"Indonesia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia_national_badminton_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia_national_badminton_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2138, \"end\": 2150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Perez_(politician)\", \"score\": 0.9999664280738939, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Daniel Perez\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Perez_(politician)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Perez_(politician)\"}, {\"begin\": 2155, \"end\": 2165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portuguese_language\", \"score\": 0.7093806911150509, \"rank\": 0.29005011254341445, \"text\": \"Portuguese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portuguese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portuguese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2179, \"end\": 2184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fidel_V._Ramos\", \"score\": 0.9999918165033861, \"rank\": 8.107869843884838e-06, \"text\": \"Ramos\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fidel_V._Ramos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fidel_V._Ramos\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If anything, I am probably more driven than I was when I started,\\\" said Smith.\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2266, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Back in Beijing, I was probably a little bit like a happy amateur: lots of talent, probably not so directed.\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2376, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2276, \"end\": 2283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999990414594369, \"rank\": 9.585415349589672e-07, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am probably in a space now where I feel like I have mastered my craft and I know what I need to do.\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2480, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The field has tightened up.\", \"from\": 2482, \"to\": 2510, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a lot more density at the top.\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2550, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just trying to keep my head above the water.\\\"\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2601, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Smith was selected as ParalympicsGB's closing ceremony flagbearer following his exploits in Tokyo, an experience he rates as the pinnacle of his career.\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2755, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2695, \"end\": 2700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.8719620234047741, \"rank\": 0.14683892942480894, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He sported an eye-catchingred and blue mohawkback then but remained tight-lipped when quizzed on his hairstyle of choice this time around.\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2895, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's all booked in but not reveals yet,\\\" said Smith.\", \"from\": 2897, \"to\": 2950, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am keeping it as modest as possible until the last possible moment - partly because I do not want the colour to wash out before the closing ceremony.\", \"from\": 2952, \"to\": 3104, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You will find out soon enough.\\\"\", \"from\": 3105, \"to\": 3136, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"PA  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3138, \"to\": 3278, \"entities\": []}]}"